# Liabilities Insurance Future Policy Expenses Gross Amount

## identifier
de4741

## type
float

## definition
Where projection techniques are used, report the net present value of Future Policy Expenses as at the relevant date, gross of ceded reinsurance, but inclusive of inwards reinsurance.

Where projection techniques are not used, report nil.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.FuturePolicyExpensesGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
